criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  The first IVF/ICSI COH cycle;

          -  the causes of infertility :fallopian tube factors and/or male factors;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Endometriosis;

          -  PCOS;

          -  Adenomyosis;

          -  PGT cycle because of the female chromosome abnormality or genetic abnormality;

          -  FET cycle;

          -  Malignant tumor patient.
